00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:16,140
Push!

875
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,710
Hurry!

876
00:36:19,350 --> 00:36:20,290
One, two!

877
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:22,590
Push! Push!

878
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,070
