in books.

906
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:24,390
That's right.

907
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,540
Is your leg hurting, Patriarch?

908
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:34,140
It's fine.

909
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:36,550
Heizi.

910
